title: Not green light 820-3115 b
message:
You can't expect Magsafe light without getting 3V42_G3H first.

I suppose you've meant L6995.
Allow 10-15s once power is removed, before measuring in diode mode.

Post U6990 voltages.

title: Not green light 820-3115 b
message:
Es un fallo clasico.
El capacitor no esta en corto puro; al aplicar tension se destruyen algunas zonas internas que indican cortos parciales.
